@startuml read_replica_routing
!include ../theme.iuml

title CQRS s read replikou: routing dotazů a replikační lag

actor "User" as u
participant "Controller" as ctrl
participant "Command Handler\n(Write)" as wh
participant "Query Handler\n(Read)" as qh
database "Primary DB\n(write model)" as primary
database "Read Replica\n(read model)" as replica

note over primary, replica
  Streaming replikace: lag 10–100 ms
  za normálních podmínek.
end note

== Write path: command jde na primary ==

u -> ctrl : POST /orders
ctrl -> wh : PlaceOrder command
wh -> primary : INSERT INTO orders…
wh -> primary : INSERT INTO outbox…
primary --> wh : OK

primary --> replica : streaming replication\n(async, ~50 ms lag)

ctrl --> u : 201 Created\n{ orderId }

== Read path: query jde na replicu ==

u -> ctrl : GET /orders/$id
ctrl -> qh : GetOrder query
qh -> replica : SELECT * FROM orders_view\nWHERE id = $id
replica --> qh : data
qh --> ctrl : view model
ctrl --> u : 200 OK

== Read-your-writes problém ==

note over u, replica
  Pokud user pošle GET ihned po POST,
  replica ještě nemá nová data → 404.
  Řešení: routing podle freshness flagu,
  nebo synchronní čtení z primary pro „read your writes".
end note

@enduml
